STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Patric D. REED-PRICE, a/k/a Patrick Price, Patrick Reed, Pat Reed, Pat Reid, Patrick D ReedPrice, Patrick D. Price, and Patrick ReedPrice, Defendant-Petitioner. C-793 September Term 2018
081947 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 4, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004249-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
